#

Creamy One-Pot Mac and Cheese

25 min
$8.5
500 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main DishComfort Food

Tags:

QuickComfort FoodKid-Friendly

Description

A quick and creamy delight that satisfies your cheesy cravings in just one pot!

Ingredients

  • elbow macaroni: 2 cups
  • cheddar cheese: 2 cups, shredded
  • milk: 2 cups
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • onion powder: 1/2 teaspoon
